title: Frieze, 1890–1920
description: Design entirely rinceau, some in a fleur-de-lis shape. Bottom edge border of silhouettes of fleur-de-lis. On a pale yellow field with vague indication of a woven pattern. Printed in gilt, white, pale green and pale yellow.

tombstone.epitaph:
Frieze, 1890–1920.
1890–1920. Machine-printed. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-84.
